{"tid":1839153,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"依場武漢肺炎 更加顯得當年曾蔭權係好特首","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:59:16.000Z","uid":58948,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf4fd09f21bcbfb54503631f80bb9e3951214fc","tid":1839153,"uid":58948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"撇除政治，拖延好多中央嘅命令<br />\n<br />\n甲型流感發生第一宗就即刻封鎖酒店，級別為嚴重<br />\n貼地咁發表評論平民衣着發表叫市民唔好恐怖<br />\n又用普通話同台灣同大陸旅客致歉（6月開始我覺得特首係已經唔識講對唔住）<br />\n當年就係菲律賓人質事件都發旅遊警示<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家推一推先行 <br />\n就算你個心係黑色，大佬你學吓曾蔭權門面野都做下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年流感報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C1BodZGoo8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC1BodZGoo8Q&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77QexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=368d840e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C1BodZGoo8Q</a>"},{"pid":"d19db606dba8de88e132cba4cbbf6dd5a80ac5c9","tid":1839153,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b8b0d6de36ed8f0c5fd91e3e6f3b25a1a2b540ae","tid":1839153,"uid":126621,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"曾蔭權俾中共清算要坐監<br />\n你覺得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有邊個特首無貪污丫<br />\n得佢要坐 因為其他都奶共"},{"pid":"5138b69e7d25e3dcbbbe68d258aee8046eed17fe","tid":1839153,"uid":77416,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020